These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, polish, german
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, analyst, software-developer
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, hot-chocolate
City: berlin, london, miami
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the brazilian is between the analyst and the software-developer##2
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the polish##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Nationality         | polish | brazilian   | german   |
| Job   | analyst     | lawyer | software-developer |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | cola    | tea      |
| City     | london     | berlin      | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, drawing, skydiving
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball, snowboarding
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, cola
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, boat
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking tea##1
5. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Hobby          | drawing  | gardening     | skydiving     |
| Sport   | volleyball     | snowboarding     | skiing      |
| Beverage   | cola  | tea | coffee |
| Transport           | boat | bike     | ship       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, pakistani, japanese
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, october, march
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, subway
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, davidoff, ritmeester
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
2. the cain-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person driving the subway##2
3. the australian is on the far left##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is the pakistani##1
5. the cain-smoker is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality          | australian  | japanese     | pakistani     |
| Birthday           | march | december  | october   |
| Transport   | skateboard  | trike    | subway |
| Cigar           | ritmeester     | cain | davidoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani, mexican
3 different games are played: bridge, whist, canasta
House: art-deco, modern, futuristic
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, cain
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the pakistani is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the mexican is between the person playing whist and the art-deco house##2
4. the pakistani is the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Nationality    | nigerian       | mexican  | pakistani   |
| Game     | whist    | canasta  | bridge |
| House     | modern   | futuristic | art-deco        |
| Cigar   | cain | ritmeester     | swisher      |

