.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, tea
City: prague, san-francisco, london
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, lilac, fuchsia
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, thai, american
1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the chinese is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person traveling to london##2
3. the person traveling to prague is the thai##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
5. the chinese is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage          | tea    | sprite     | water      |
| City         | prague | san-francisco | london |
| Color   | fuchsia  | lilac       | yellow       |
| Nationality           | thai     | chinese       | american     |

