2. the person who growspoppy is the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who growsorchid and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Flower          | orchid | begonia | poppy    |
| City         | london | colone      | miami |
| Birthday   | september   | october     | july        |
