.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, pakistani, nigerian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, february, december
3 different pets are kept: pony, ferret, goldfish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, juice, lemonade
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the nigerian and the person drinking water##2
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in december and the owner of the pony##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Nationality          | nigerian      | pakistani   | turkish |
| Birthday         | june | february | december |
| Pet   | pony      | goldfish | ferret   |
| Beverage     | lemonade         | juice  | water       |

