.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, azalea, bellflower
3 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, family-climbing
3 different games are played: go, monopoly, backgammon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, animation, family
1. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person playing go is between the owner of the fish and the person who growsbellflower##2
5. the person who growsazalea is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Flower      | lily       | azalea      | bellflower      |
| Pet         | fish    | family-climbing | ferret      |
| Game           | backgammon | go     | monopoly |
| Movie-Genre   | animation     | family          | mystery       |

