.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, rowing, cricket
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, mechanic, security-guard
House: craftsman, farmhouse, modern
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, prince, dunhill
1. the dunhill-smoker is between the farmhouse house and the modern house##2
2. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
4. the mechanic is on the far left##1
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
6. the prince-smoker is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Sport      | lacrosse      | rowing | cricket     |
| Job          | mechanic   | nurse      | security-guard     |
| House   | modern  | craftsman      | farmhouse |
| Cigar     | bluemaster | dunhill        | prince     |

