2. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the owner of the rat is the person traveling to rome##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the tiparillo-smoker is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Birthday       | june       | january       | july    |
| City         | rome | miami | nizza |
| Pet       | rat      | chinchilla         | turtle |
| Cigar   | tiparillo        | vegafina            | game  |

