1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the lawyer##1
3. the accountant is in the middle##1
4. the accountant is between the person playing whist and the person playing domino##2
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
6. the person playing domino is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
