.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, coral, amber
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily, begonia
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, soccer, skiing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, may, july
1. the person who likes coral is the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who likes coral is between the person who growslily and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Color      | emerald | coral      | amber            |
| Flower           | zinnia | begonia | lily |
| Sport   | soccer     | skiing        | rugby         |
| Birthday   | may  | october    | july        |

