3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the malaysian##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the spanish##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| City      | san-francisco    | colone          | rome |
| Transport          | trike | bike           | skateboard        |
| Hobby           | photography | hiking | fishing         |
| Nationality   | polish    | malaysian    | spanish      |

