1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to boston is between the person who's birthday is in june and the montecristo-smoker##2
3. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
4. the person playing snooker is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person playing monopoly##2
5. the person who's birthday is in december is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
