.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
3 different games are played: domino, scrabble, go
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, mauve, red
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, tea
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, social-worker, fisherman
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the person who likes red is between the designer and the person who likes light-blue##2
3. the person playing go is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the designer##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person playing domino##1
6. the person playing domino is on the left of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Game       | go | domino | scrabble |
| Color         | light-blue   | red       | mauve        |
| Beverage       | tea | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate         |
| Job   | fisherman    | social-worker     | designer         |

