.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
City: new-york, nizza, edinburgh
House: wooden, palace, futuristic
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, dancing, traveling
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, yellow, mauve
1. the palace house is between the person who likes mauve and the wooden house##2
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person traveling to new-york##1
5. the person who likes brown is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the wooden house is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| City   | nizza | new-york  | edinburgh     |
| House   | futuristic    | palace | wooden |
| Hobby           | drawing        | traveling   | dancing  |
| Color     | mauve      | yellow   | brown |

