House: tower, craftsman, gothic-revival
City: hamburg, miami, new-york
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, rock-climbing, writing
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the gothic-revival house is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the craftsman house##1
5. the tower house is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking fanta and the person traveling to miami##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage           | lemonade   | 7up   | fanta |
| House   | gothic-revival | craftsman   | tower     |
| City   | miami     | hamburg      | new-york    |
| Hobby           | baking | rock-climbing | writing    |

