.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, sailing
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, manager, accountant
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, yellow, grey
House: cape-cod, futuristic, modern
1. the futuristic house is the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the accountant##1
3. the person who likes brown is between the person who's sport is cycling and the journalist##2
4. the person who likes yellow is the modern house##1
5. the cape-cod house is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who likes yellow##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing     | ice-hockey        |
| Job         | manager   | accountant | journalist |
| Color   | yellow        | brown       | grey      |
| House           | modern           | cape-cod    | futuristic       |

