.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, ivory, chestnut
City: paris, nizza, hannover
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, game, dannemann
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, iris, daffodil
1. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the game-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the game-smoker is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is between the person who growsdaffodil and the game-smoker##2
6. the dannemann-smoker is the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Color        | ivory      | lavender | chestnut |
| City         | nizza     | hannover    | paris        |
| Cigar       | game | dannemann   | old-henry   |
| Flower   | balloon-flower          | iris     | daffodil       |

 